Notes: Jennies No. 15 in NCAA Division II
Head Coach Dave Slifer gets his 400th career win as a college basketball coach
Tiffany Vincent and Lindsey Maple lead CMSU with 17 points apiece.  Maple goes
5-of-6 from the free throw line in the final :40 to ice the win.
Game.Officials: Greg Small,  Randy Dillon,  and Lisa Pitts
